{"tid":1559560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這是最壞的時代，這是最好的時代；支撐義士背後的義務律師","createTime":"2019-09-11T01:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T01:39:49.000Z","uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb71f0dfdfb801443aaf195ce806c1d8b1c1bca","tid":1559560,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:04:11.000Z","msg":"記：你覺得香港總有無希望？<br />\n黃：香港慶幸仍然總有香港人，香港仍然總有班好可愛嘅香港人。<br />\n<br />\n這是最黑暗的時代，亦是最光輝的時代。<br />\n政府愈製造白色恐怖，愈代表開始技窮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/453539841327141/posts/2842979119049856/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F453539841327141%2Fposts%2F2842979119049856%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRei8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=c462eb4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/453539841327141/posts/2842979119049856/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每一個示威者都有佢自己嘅故事，每接觸一個示威者都係一次好深刻嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n香港法治係呢3個月迅速咁崩潰，好大程度上鄭若嬅同刑事專員都要負上責任。無佢地背後撐腰，深信警隊一個人唔會咁放肆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/453539841327141/posts/2842975069050261/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F453539841327141%2Fposts%2F2842975069050261%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRei8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=fc333941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/453539841327141/posts/2842975069050261/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我無嘢講，我無必要同你傾計，我有權利去唔簽任何文件。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/453539841327141/posts/2842799075734527/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F453539841327141%2Fposts%2F2842799075734527%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRei8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=7d2dc0a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/453539841327141/posts/2842799075734527/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a68fd83c1a88b7920c88bb